{"tid":1312254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日去沙田發夢/野餐嘅，請做足安全措施","createTime":"2019-07-13T13:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T00:16:20.000Z","uid":131691,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d14f2118caaf0533b7d64c8a1e73d0a5f1c3eff4","tid":1312254,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:03:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱訓完晏覺<br />\n痴撚線<br />\n啲社會垃圾已經完全失控<br />\n行緊街就已經派胡椒豬肚湯<br />\n亂衝，9衝，亂打，9打<br />\n<br />\n所以聽日，就算淨係諗住安靜享受野餐嘅人，都要做足安全措施<br />\n就算自己用唔着，都可以交俾有需要嘅人<br />\n<br />\n雨傘（not縮骨）<br />\n勞工手套<br />\n生理鹽水<br />\n頭盔<br />\n眼罩<br />\n口罩<br />\n<br />\n今日真心痴線，真係冇差別打人<br />\n<br />\n不過唔知點解<br />\n反而令到我更加想發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3613b9f60e899d8dce4512d3a1d9a210a2b12b","tid":1312254,"uid":59922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:04:32.000Z","msg":"cover 好手腳頸眼<br />\npepper spray好辣㗎<br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話有梘液溝水沖患處"},{"pid":"4fc8c67b75e635544dba89540ba972d5cedbf506","tid":1312254,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得保護自己"},{"pid":"b2d82a4e33e3f8ac29f0163af984bc9355fc1345","tid":1312254,"uid":8075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:05:58.000Z","msg":"不如沖定梘液溝水過去 比中椒嘅手足用啦"},{"pid":"658eadd7e744c4d4fdbfcc04dc20661e8e0890f4","tid":1312254,"uid":207297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce3613b9f60e899d8dce4512d3a1d9a210a2b12b","tid":1312254,"uid":59922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:04:32.000Z","msg":"cover 好手腳頸眼<br />\npepper spray好辣㗎<br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話有梘液溝水沖患處"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"搭單一問，梳打水係咪都ok?"},{"pid":"53b961c65ed122b499972883c293ef30b9f06512","tid":1312254,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"658eadd7e744c4d4fdbfcc04dc20661e8e0890f4","tid":1312254,"uid":2072